
  Sealeo    Ice Type Pokémon

  SEALEO has the habit of always 
  juggling on the tip of its nose 
  anything it sees for the first 
  time.  Sealeo occasionally 
  entertains itself by balancing 
  and rolling a SPHEAL on its nose. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Spheal ► Sealeo ► Walrein

